Label: Description
Value: OpenStreetMap exports for use in GIS applications. This theme includes all OpenStreetMap features in this area matching ( Learn what tags means here ) : tags['aeroway'] IS NOT NULL OR tags['building'] = 'aerodrome' OR tags['emergency:helipad'] IS NOT NULL OR tags['emergency'] = 'landing_site' Features may have these attributes:  name name:en aeroway building emergency emergency:helipad operator:type capacity:persons addr:full addr:city source name:es  This dataset is one of many OpenStreetMap exports on HDX. See the Humanitarian OpenStreetMap Team website for more information.

Label: Caveats/Comments
